#: script_checking/error_database.csv
msgid "You get this error when the name between the [code]for[/code] and [code]in[/code] is not a valid variable name, or you are missing the [code]in[/code] keyword."
msgstr "當 [code]for[/code] 和 [code]in[/code] 之間的名稱不是有效的變數名稱，或是你遺漏了 [code]in[/code] 關鍵字時，會出現這個錯誤。"

#: script_checking/error_database.csv
#, fuzzy
msgid " the [code]in[/code] keyword only accepts a valid temporary variable name to assign values in each loop iteration. The loop creates a new variable with the desired name and assigns each element of the array to it.\""
msgstr "在 [code]for[/code] 迴圈中， [code]in[/code] 關鍵字只接受一個有效的臨時變數名稱，並將每次迴圈的值指定給該變數。這個迴圈會創建一個新的變數並將陣列中的每個元素依照順序指定給它。"

#: script_checking/error_database.csv
#, fuzzy
msgid "To fix this error, you need to ensure that the name between the [code]for[/code] and [code]in[/code] keywords is a valid variable name with no punctuation or spaces"
msgstr "要修正這個錯誤，你需要確保 [code]for[/code] 和 [code]in[/code] 之間的名稱是有效的變數名稱，且不包含標點符號或空格。"

#: script_checking/error_database.csv
#, fuzzy
