#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Orders the robot to play an animation."
msgstr "命令機器人播放動畫。"

#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Selects units in the cell coordinates passed as the function's argument."
msgstr "選擇作為函式參數傳入的儲存格座標上的單位。"

#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Queues a move animation towards the target cell."
msgstr "將移動到目標儲存格的動畫加入佇列。"

#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Adds the value passed as an argument at the back of the array."
msgstr "將作為參數傳入的值新增到該陣列的末尾。"

#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Removes the first value from the array and returns it."
msgstr "刪除該陣列中的第一個值，並將其返回。"

#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Removes the last value from the array and returns it."
msgstr "刪除該陣列中的最後一個值，並將其返回。"

#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Returns the argument converted into a [code]String[/code]. Works with the majority of value types."
msgstr "返回轉換為 [code]String[/code] 後的參數。支援大部分數值型別。"

#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Returns the argument converted into an [code]int[/code] (whole number) [i]if possible[/i]. Supports converting decimal numbers, strings, and booleans. Useful to convert player text input into numbers."
msgstr "[b]如果可能[/b]，返回轉換為 [code]int[/code]（整數）後的參數。支援轉換小數、字串、布林值。可用於將玩家輸入的文字轉換為數位。"

#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Creates a new unit matching the type parameter and places it at the desired cell position on the game grid."
msgstr "新建一個單位，與類型參數相匹配，放置於遊戲網格內所需的儲存格位置上。"

#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Creates a new item and displays it in the inventory."
msgstr "新建一個道具並在背包中顯示。"

#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Increases the item count by amount."
msgstr "增加指定數量的道具。"

#: course/documentation.csv
msgid "Realigns the train track with the path. Select a train track in the tracks array by index to pass it as an argument."
msgstr ""

msgid "Learn to Code From Zero with Godot"
msgstr ""

#~ msgid "Another possibility is that you want to check for equality in a condition but wrote a single = instead of ==."
#~ msgstr "另一個可能性是，你想要在條件判斷中檢查相等性，但錯誤地寫成單個 [code]=[/code] 而不是 [code]==[/code]。"

#~ msgid "You also need to ensure the syntax is correct. For example, there shouldn't be parentheses on the left side of the equal sign."
#~ msgstr "你還需要確保語法正確。例如，等號左邊不應該有括號。"

#~ msgid "In the case of a condition, ensure that you are using two equal signs to check for equality (==)."
#~ msgstr "在條件判斷中，確保你使用的是兩個等號來檢查是否相等 (==)。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "1. You used the class name in the class itself.\n"
#~ "2. Your code refers to another class that refers to this class, causing an endless reference cycle."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "1. 你在類別內部使用了類別自己。\n"
#~ "2. 你的程式碼引用了另一個類別，而該類別又引用了這個類別，造成無限循環引用。"

#~ msgid "Erase the type hint in the error line, and the problem should disappear."
#~ msgstr "刪除錯誤行中的類型提示，問題應該就會消失。"

#~ msgid "The computer uses those leading tab characters on code lines to know which lines of code are part of a code block, like a function."
#~ msgstr "電腦利用這些行首的 tab 字符來識別程式碼行是否屬於某個程式區塊，例如一個函式。"

#~ msgid "Note that this error can appear [b]after[/b] the line causing it due to how the computer reads and analyzes your code."
#~ msgstr "請注意，由於電腦讀取和分析程式碼的方式，這個錯誤可能會出現在 [b]造成錯誤的行之後[/b]。"

#~ msgid "Three keywords in GDScript work like function calls and require parentheses: [code]yield()[/code], [code]preload()[/code], and [code]assert()[/code]."
#~ msgstr "在 GDScript 中，有三個關鍵字像函式呼叫一樣，並需要括號： [code]yield()[/code], [code]preload()[/code] 和 [code]assert()[/code]。"

#~ msgid "This error tells you are missing some parenthesis, a comma, or some value in your export hint."
#~ msgstr "這個錯誤告訴你在導出提示中缺少了某個括號、逗號或某個值。"

#~ msgid "You need to read the error message and add the missing character or value it requests."
#~ msgstr "你需要閱讀錯誤訊息，並根據它的要求添加缺少的字符或值。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "1. You wrote an identifier (variable or function name) in the wrong place.\n"
#~ "2. You wrote a keyword like [code]var[/code], [code]func[/code], [code]for[/code], or [code]signal[/code], and you did not follow it by a name.\n"
#~ "3. You wrote a function definition but forgot the parentheses before the colon."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "1. 你把識別符（變數或函式名稱）寫錯位置。\n"
#~ "2. 你寫了像 [code]var[/code], [code]func[/code], [code]for[/code] 或 [code]signal[/code] 這樣的關鍵字，但後面沒有接名稱。\n"
#~ "3. 你寫了函式定義，但忘記在冒號之前加上括號。"

#~ msgid "If the error says you have something unexpected, you are likely missing a keyword like [code]var[/code], [code]func[/code], [code]for[/code], etc."
#~ msgstr "如果錯誤告訴你有意外情況，那麼你很可能漏寫了像 [code]var[/code]、[code]func[/code]、[code]for[/code] 等關鍵字。"

#~ msgid "Another possibility is that you need to write a colon at the end of a function definition, [code]for[/code] loop, or a line starting with [code]if[/code], [code]elif[/code], or [code]else[/code]."
#~ msgstr "另一種可能是，你需要在函式定義、[code]for[/code] 迴圈，或以 [code]if[/code]、[code]elif[/code] 或 [code]else[/code] 開頭的條件語句後加上冒號。"

#~ msgid "It also occurs when you write an arrow ([code]->[/code]) after the parentheses of a function definition but do not follow it with a type name."
#~ msgstr "它也會發生在你在函式定義的括號後寫了箭頭（[code]->[/code]），但沒有加上類型名稱時。"

#~ msgid "You most often get this error when you make typos. Maybe you swapped two letters, forgot a letter... sometimes, it's hard to spot."
#~ msgstr "當你打錯字時，通常會出現這個錯誤。也許你交換了兩個字母、忘了寫一個字母……有時候很難發現。"

#~ msgid "The other cause for this error is that you didn't define the variable, function, or class you're trying to access."
#~ msgstr "這個錯誤的另一個原因是你沒有定義你正在嘗試存取的變數、函式或類別。"

#~ msgid "The [code]continue[/code] keyword means \"jump to the next iteration of the loop.\" And the [code]break[/code] keyword means \"end the loop right now and jump to the first line of code after the loop block."
#~ msgstr "[code]continue[/code] 關鍵字的意思是「跳到下一次的迴圈執行」。而 [code]break[/code] 關鍵字則表示「立即結束這個迴圈，並跳到迴圈區塊之後的第一行程式碼」。"

#~ msgid "You can also use arithmetic operators like multiplications (*), additions (+), and so on."
#~ msgstr "您也可以使用算術運算子，例如乘法（*）、加法（+）等等。"

#~ msgid "We typically write class names in PascalCase: with a capital letter at the start of every word that composes the class name."
#~ msgstr "我們通常使用 PascalCase 來書寫類別名稱：每個單字的首字母皆大寫。"

#~ msgid "You can optionally use numbers in the name, but not in the first position."
#~ msgstr "您可以選擇在名稱中使用數字，但不能將數字放在名稱的第一個位置。"

#~ msgid "Perhaps the function or variable already exists in the current code file, but it may also be in a parent class that this GDScript code extends."
#~ msgstr "這個函式或變數可能已經存在於當前的程式碼檔案中，也有可能是存在於此 GDScript 程式碼所繼承的父類別中。"

#~ msgid "For example, if the parent has two arguments, you need your new function also to have two arguments. If you use type hints in your function definitions, the argument types must match the parent class."
#~ msgstr "舉例來說，如果父類別的函式有兩個參數，您的新函式也必須有兩個參數。若您的函式定義使用了型別註記（type hints），則參數的型別必須與父類別一致。"

#~ msgid "You'll need to read the error message to see what is not matching because there are many possible cases."
#~ msgstr "由於可能出現多種型別錯誤，您需要仔細閱讀錯誤訊息，以確認哪個型別不匹配，然後進行適當的轉換或調整。"

#~ msgid "If the computer talks about an invalid operand, then the issue is that the operation does not exist for the type you're trying to use. For example, while you can add two 2D vectors, you can't add a whole number or text to a 2D vector."
#~ msgstr "如果系統提示無效的運算元，代表你嘗試執行的運算不適用於該類型。例如，雖然可以相加兩個 2D 向量，但無法將整數或文字加到 2D 向量上。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "1. Your function is a void function, thus it should not return a value. This includes functions with the '-> void' syntax and class constructors ('_init()').\n"
#~ "2. You specified a return type for your function, but you are not returning a value in all possible branches (if, elif, and else blocks) or at the end."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "1. 你的函式是無回傳值函式，因此不應該回傳任何值。這包括使用 '-> void' 語法的函式和類別建構子（'_init()'）。\n"
#~ "2. 你為函式指定了回傳類型，但在所有可能的分支（if、elif 和 else 區塊）或最後並沒有回傳值。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The computer reached the end of the line of code, but the line had a syntax error.\n"
#~ "The most common case is when you forget to close a string: you have opening quotes, but you forget to add a matching closing quote."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "系統已經到達程式碼的結尾，但該行存在語法錯誤。\n"
#~ "最常見的情況是你忘記閉合字串：你有開啟的引號，但忘記加上匹配的閉合引號。"

